Artist's Notes
--------------
HARVEY.SEQ was created by Eric Jolley.  Its full title is:

"One-Eyed Harvey:  Portrait 1 of the Ship's Computer (With 
Flickering Diode)"

It's a sort of abstract art of computer animations.  If you like it, 
good, if you don't, that's OK too.

